              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>Although we do not explore it in <fr:link href="/jms-00XY/" title="IA Discrete Mathematics" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00XY/" display-uri="jms-00XY" type="local">this course</fr:link>, the viewpoint of matrix multiplication as relational composition generalises to a correct explanation of the role of matrices in geometry as presentations of linear maps between vector spaces in terms of an (uncanonical) choice of basis.</html:p>
